desc.html: Pictured taken after Celine Chen's first major fashion show in 1991, at the White Swan Hotel in Guangzhou. Celine Chen is in light blue dress (2nd from the left). The man standing next to Chen is 霍震霆, while the lady standing next to Celine is the former wife of 霍震霆- 朱玲玲. Man in yellow is currently a prominent Chinese fashion designer- 刘洋. Lady on the far right is 黄谷穗, currently one of the top ten fashion designers in China.

wiki.Credit: Pic taken after the fashion show took place in 1991. Pic was later scanned into the computer.
